node.text:
We tried @steakout for the 2nd time and once again, it didn’t disappoint! 🤤😋 For starters, We had the Dirty Fries and Prawn Dippers! 🤤 The Dirty Fries from @steakout still remain the best i have ever had! 👑 For mains, we had the Filet Mignon which was so soft and tender 😍 and the Buttermilk Chicken Burger 🍔😋 Definitely recommend to checkout @steakout 

TAG YOUR FRIENDS BELOW! 👇👇👇
